# SPARC pipeline run outputs (keep tool_specs + scripts, ignore generated result
# trees and large per-trace inputs).  The output*/ glob covers all per-track,
# per-mode, and per-version variants (output, output_fast_track_runtime,
# output_slow_track_eval_v2, output_round2_*, …).
scripts/runs/*/output*/
scripts/runs/*/input/
scripts/output/
scripts/sample_traces/

# Comparison + analysis notes (regenerated locally, large)
scripts/runs/COMPARISON*.md
scripts/runs/JUDGEMENT_ANALYSIS.md